---

<Layout title="Champion Studs | Maxline Bulldogs" description="Meet our cinematic lineup of AKC Champion Mini English Bulldogs. Each stud embodies legendary film characters: Joker, Nirvana, Hannibal, The Substance, The Sandman, and Harley Quinn.">
